snippet: Ben Crane won the St. Jude Classic by a stroke Sunday for his first PGA Tour title since 2011, despite closing with a three-over-par 73.
abstract: Ben Crane wins St Jude Classic golf tournament at TPC Southwind in Memphis; other golf news and developments noted.
lead_paragraph: Ben Crane won the St. Jude Classic by a stroke Sunday for his first PGA Tour title since 2011, despite closing with a three-over-par 73.
